    <note>Liu(2) Shi [1226] His ancestors were Pengcheng jun Liu(2). They moved to Jizhou, Luling xian to avoid the disturbances at the end of the Jin dynasty and subsequently moved to Linjiang, Xinyu xian before the end of the Tang. He received his degree at the end of the Southern Tang. Lizhi's [1207], Lili's [1208], and Lide's [1209] father, Ban's [1220] grandfather, Fengshi's [1195] and Dangshi's [1235] great grandfather. See entry for wife in CBD, 5, 3844 as well as documentation for 6th generation descendant, Su(3) [13241]. XCB, 30.24a, 40.11a-11b, 11b (n.); Liu Chang, WJ, 51.1a; SHY:ZG, 5.24a, 24b; SS, 267.14a-14b; Du Dagui, 'zhong,' 40.6b-8a. CBD, 5, 3843-44.</note>
